# General Calculator

A simple calculator program that performs various arithmetic and statistical operations.

## Features

- Supports basic arithmetic operations: addition (+), subtraction (-), multiplication (*), division (/), exponentiation (**)
- Calculates Body Mass Index (BMI)
- Performs statistical operations: max, min, sum, mean, median, mode, range, and dispersion (variance and standard deviation)
- Enables input of numbers separated by commas for statistical analysis.

## Usage
1. Run the program and select an operation from the menu.
2. Enter the required inputs when prompted, based on your chosen operation.
3. The program will display the result of the operation.
4. You can continue performing operations or exit the program by entering "Stop".

## Operations
- Arithmetic Operations: You can perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, exponentiation, and find roots.
- BMI Calculation: Input your height (in meters) and weight (in kilograms) to calculate your BMI.
- Other Statistics: Choose from operations like Max, Min, Sum, Range, Sort, Central (Mean, Median, Mode), and Dispersion (Variance, Standard Deviation).